<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <% include 'head.ect' %>
        <title>DataFed Login</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="col-flex ui-widget-content" style="height:100%;border:none">
            <div class="ui-widget-header" style="border:none;flex:none;padding:0.2em .5em">
                <span class='ui-icon ui-icon-box' style='vertical-align:middle;color:white;font-size:1.6em'></span>
                <span style="font-size:1.8em;vertical-align:middle">&nbsp;Scientific Data Federation</span>
                <div style='float:right;padding:.2em 0 0 0'>
                    <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://ornl.github.io/DataFed/','datafed-docs')">Help</button>&nbsp<button class="btn" onclick="location.href='/ui/login'">Log In / Register</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="flex:auto;overflow:auto">
            <div style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;margin:2em auto 1em auto;width:40em">
                <div style='font-size:250%;margin-bottom:1em'>Welcome to DataFed!</div>

                <div style='font-size:110%'>
                <p>The <i>Scientific Data Federation</i> is a network of scientific data repositories located across the
                    scientific user facilities operated by the Department of Energy.</p>
                    
                <p><i>DataFed</i> is the "engine" that drives this data network, and, with it, scientists can easily access,
                    organize, and share <b>big data</b> across facilities while benefiting from increased productivity and
                    scientific reproducibility.</p>
                </div>

                <div style='margin: 3em auto 3em auto;width:34em'>
                    <button class="btn btn-welcome" onclick="location.href='/ui/login'">Log-In To Web Portal</button>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    <button class="btn btn-welcome" onclick="location.href='/ui/login'">Register For An Account</button>
                </div>

                <h3>What is DataFed, Exactly?</h3>

                <p>DataFed is a domain-agnostic, scientific data management system (SDMS) that federates data storage
                    resources (located at DOE facilities) into a single, unified data access paradigm. DataFed relies
                    on <a href="https://www.globus.org/">Globus</a> for high-performance, reliable, and secure data
                    transport between (and within) facilities. For more information about DataFed, click the button
                    below.</p>

                <div style='margin: 3em auto 3em auto;width:17em'>
                    <button class="btn btn-welcome" onclick="window.open('https://ornl.github.io/DataFed/','datafed-docs')">Learn More About DataFed</button>
                </div>

                <h3>Registration</h3>
                <p>DataFed registration is free, but a Globus account with a linked GlobusID identity is required to
                    access DataFed. If you don't have a Globus account, or haven't linked a GlobusID identity, please
                    sign-up (for free) at <a href="https://www.globusid.org/">GlobusID.org</a> then return to this page to
                    register for DataFed access.</p>
                <h3>Web Browser Compatibility</h3>
                <p>The DataFed web application requires an HTML5 compliant web browser. <i>Chrome, Firefox,</i> and <i>Safari</i>
                    have been validated for use with DataFed.
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ui-widget-header" style="flex:none;padding:.25em">
                User: Not Logged In
                <div style='float:right'><span id='mode_label' class='ui-state-error'></span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <script>
        window.name = 'sdms_target';
        $(".btn").button();


        var g_test_mode = "<%- @test_mode %>";
        if ( g_test_mode ){
            $("#mode_label").html("<b>DEV MODE</b>");
        }

    </script>
</html>
